Scoutsuite Installation on AWS


sudo curl "https://awscli.amazonaws.com/awscli-exe-linux-x86_64.zip" -o "awscliv2.zip"

sudo apt install unzip

sudo unzip awscliv2.zip

sudo ./aws/install

aws --version

aws configure

Access key ID     : AKIAZYQWCKRC6AEOR674          

Secret access key : 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

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install python3-virtualenv

git clone https://github.com/nccgroup/ScoutSuite.git

cd ScoutSuite

virtualenv -p python3 venv

source venv/bin/activate

pip install scoutsuite

 scout -h aws --region us-east-1

 scout aws
 
Install a tool called WinSCP to tranfer the file generated in the linux machine into windows machine.
The public ip v4 address along with the private key ie., .ppk file is required to establish the connection between EC2 linux machine and the windows machine.
